[{"id":"VR184678","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows the graph of eight point charges that form a cube in the x y z coordinate space. Each point charge is located at one of the corners of the cube. The cube is oriented so that one corner is at the origin, and the three edges from that corner are on the x axis, y axis, and z axis respectively. The four point charges on the corners of the bottom face of the cube, which is in the x z plane, each have charge positive q. The four point charges on the corners of the top face of the cube, which is parallel to the x z plane but above it along the y axis, each have charge negative q.\" height=\"301\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VR184678.g03.png\" width=\"300\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Charges of equal magnitude are placed at the corners of a cube, with charges of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative q\"><math alttext=\"negative q\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>q</mi></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> at the top and charges of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive q\"><math alttext=\"positive q\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>q</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> at the bottom, as shown in the figure above. If a positive charge is placed at the center of the cube, what is the direction of the force on it due to the other charges?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR184678_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive x\"><math alttext=\"positive x\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive y\"><math alttext=\"positive y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative y\"><math alttext=\"negative y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive z\"><math alttext=\"positive z\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>z</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative z\"><math alttext=\"negative z\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>z</mi></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":1}]